96
00:09:16,960 --> 00:09:18,760
<font color="#16F158">Marsz do domu, matka!</font>

97
00:09:18,920 --> 00:09:20,720
<font color="#16F158">Raz-raz!</font>

98
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:27,920
